<span id="freeTextContainer3129078355369428778">I wanted to love this, but unfortunately I just didn&apos;t. Though a fairly quick read, it was kind of boring. From what I&apos;ve seen and read, the movie is much better than the book so I&apos;m hoping to watch that soon. For me, it all boils down to the fact that I was pretty bored while reading this. I read it quickly, but I wasn&apos;t interested at all. I just kept reading to get to the end and have it be over, which is not how you want to feel while reading a book.<br/><br/>Maybe I&apos;ll like the movie more, we&apos;ll see.</span>
